    <item>
      <title>贝宁发行美元债券，标志着非洲今年首次发行债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/benin-s-dollar-bond-marks-africa-s-first-debt-sale-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝宁正在准备为美元债券发行定价，为今年非洲首次发行主权债券奠定基础。消息一经公布，这个西非国家现有的欧元债券价格飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/benin-s-dollar-bond-marks-africa-s-first-debt-sale-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 13:13:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行官员认为，若维持基准利率，进一步宽松政策将更为合适</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/ecb-officials-saw-more-easing-as-appropriate-if-baseline-holds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行上次政策决议报告显示，央行官员判断，如果消费者物价走势符合预期，利率可能进一步下调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/ecb-officials-saw-more-easing-as-appropriate-if-baseline-holds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 12:56:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非政府考虑让国有企业上市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/south-african-government-considers-listing-state-owned-firms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非政府表示，正与约翰内斯堡证券交易所密切合作，将该国陷入困境的国有企业在主要交易所上市，以促进投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/south-african-government-considers-listing-state-owned-firms</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 12:47:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
